{"tid":2493887,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"菲臘親王疫下與女皇耍花槍勁甜蜜 「傻婆收聲！」「我是女皇！」","createTime":"2021-04-18T08:48:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T13:39:14.000Z","uid":361987,"like":31,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6e3b173ee488079421d2b12ce00f8963e3f09673","tid":2493887,"uid":361987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:48:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jnfEmtOfSO2knct-Pscdy4UWDC0=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TILD4L6FZRF2NNLFJDLQONRXD4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjnfEmtOfSO2knct-Pscdy4UWDC0%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTILD4L6FZRF2NNLFJDLQONRXD4.jpg&h=4bb3f8e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國菲臘親王的喪禮周六舉行，女皇在聖佐治教堂單獨就座、形單影隻的畫面叫人格外傷感。皇室侍從透露，過去一年多女皇與菲臘親王因疫情避居溫莎堡期間，兩夫婦不時「耍花槍」，例如一次菲臘親王曾喚女皇為「傻婆」，要她住口，女皇則回道「我是女皇」，可惜一切都隨着菲臘親王逝世成為回憶。<br />\n<br />\n女皇與菲臘親王結婚70多年，但過去兩人都經常出席公務，實際相處時間不多，直至疫情期間皇室公務大幅減少，使她與菲臘親王得以在溫莎堡朝夕相對。儘管女皇和菲臘親王都年近百歲，但二人仍如膠似漆，一方面互相支持，不時也有小爭執。<br />\n<br />\n侍從憶述一次女皇和菲臘親王因小事鬥嘴起來，當時菲臘親王說道「噢，住口吧，你這傻婆」，女皇則「駁嘴」說：「我才不是傻婆，我是女皇」。該名侍從形容女皇和菲臘親王「就是在鬥嘴，真是令人意想不到地甜蜜&hellip;&hellip;我不能相信自己的耳朵，但其他侍從也說，這就是他們日常相處的方式」。<br />\n<br />\n疫下朝夕相對 最後時光常回憶往事<br />\n<br />\n《每日郵報》皇室記者凱伊（Richard Kay）引述消息人士指，菲臘親王早前留院一個月後回到溫莎堡，但精神已變得很差，經常感到疲倦和想睡覺，女皇在這段最後時光，與菲臘親王「瘋了似的回憶舊事」，經常回看一家人的照片，又翻看陳年電影，二人亦時常談天說地，不過女皇一次提議回看菲臘親王昔日畫下的油畫時，菲臘親王則堅決不願意。<br />\n<br />\n皇室侍從表示，女皇日後會較多居於溫莎堡，只在工作時使用白金漢宮，但相信不會再在白金漢宮留宿，意味今後首相覲見女皇時需前往較遠的溫莎。<br />\n<br />\n英國《星期日鏡報》/英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210418/FEMZGTF3KBEE3ELTWH44U5HOVE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210418%2FFEMZGTF3KBEE3ELTWH44U5HOVE%2F&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RH88up93QrsUiEJqOxYGoBw%3D&h=264b0ac1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210418%2FFEMZGTF3KBEE3ELTWH44U5HOVE%2F&h=78085f42\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210418/FEMZGTF3KBEE3ELTWH44U5HOVE/</a>"},{"pid":"2e724161a972bda210242f5bd09ce528055fdb98","tid":2493887,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:53:12.000Z","msg":"sweet<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be6e1f37878055988064ed96e66b0681901b1302","tid":2493887,"uid":99962,"like":36,"dislike":9,"score":27,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:53:42.000Z","msg":"林生：收手啦傻婆<br />\n<br />\n林太，我唔係傻婆，我係特首"},{"pid":"9bd16d00740a639443ed21c57fbfeee5660e81a0","tid":2493887,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:54:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"607a64ee83cb1c4ee3f81c825b67b3acfc184dbd","tid":2493887,"uid":20514,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"be6e1f37878055988064ed96e66b0681901b1302","tid":2493887,"uid":99962,"like":36,"dislike":9,"score":27,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:53:42.000Z","msg":"林生：收手啦傻婆<br />\n<br />\n林太，我唔係傻婆，我係特首"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:57:45.000Z","msg":"收手啦柒婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4605c1a62b8c12fd2560a7cf8aaafd2e35d1fdad","tid":2493887,"uid":61994,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"be6e1f37878055988064ed96e66b0681901b1302","tid":2493887,"uid":99962,"like":36,"dislike":9,"score":27,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:53:42.000Z","msg":"林生：收手啦傻婆<br />\n<br />\n林太，我唔係傻婆，我係特首"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:59:02.000Z","msg":"叫我習鄭"},{"pid":"45e65ba4a60959d4e0ea9929a464f244652765de","tid":2493887,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be6e1f37878055988064ed96e66b0681901b1302","tid":2493887